MBH feedback is\nrequired to interpret the X-ray emission in this region.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 6 Jul 2016 11:09:48 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 6 Sep 2016 22:49:26 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 1 Aug 2017 18:00:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-08-09"}
