sics models and it\nprovides the necessary basis for realistic modelling of neutron stars.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 6 Jul 2016 14:14:30 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 24 Jan 2017 17:36:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-01-25"}
